wikipedia_page.main: Robert Terence Traynor (born 1 November 1983) is an English retired semi-professional football forward who made over 210 appearances in the Isthmian League for Kingstonian. He began his career in the Football League with Brentford, before dropping into non-league football upon his release in 2004.
